    "When used quantitatively, the model has been found to describe 74% of variance in behavioural intention to use technology (Venkatesh et al., 2016).",
    "The high explanatory power of the model and its capacity to provide a qualitative model for examining teacher motivations (e.g.",
    "Bower et al., 2020) has led to it being used as an a-priori framework for coding teacher motivations in this study.",
    "The objective of this study was to understand whether teachers believe that generative AI tools such as ChatGPT will impact on teaching and assessment, and if so, how.",
